description:
#shorts 
The last 7 plagues have struck fear and intrigue in the minds of Bible scholars for thousands of years. This will be the greatest time of trouble and disaster the world has ever seen, and we are now closer than ever to these earth-shattering events. What are these 7 plagues? Who will be struck by them? And most importantly  how can YOU avoid them! Dont miss this one friend!
